Title: Zarak Mosadek (No. 23)
Writer: Jon Bokenkamp (created by), Sean Hennen, Marisa Tam (story editor), Taylor Martin (story editor), Dave Metzger (staff writer)
Actors: James Spader, Megan Boone, Diego Klattenhoff, Amir Arison
Plot: Red and the Task Force head to Paris in hopes of pressuring Garvey by taking down a prominent heroin supplier to the Nash Syndicate. Liz doesn't trust Red and takes her own path to find Garvey.
